content: I don't see an option for already voted. What should I mark down?
If you don't know who they voted for you can mark it refused. If they voted Harris you can mark strong Harris and skip sending a text with voting info
Gotcha ok thank you! The person I spoke to voted dem down ballot so was good to hear!
Awesome! Love to hear it! Thank you for being here and making calls with us! <a:bluewave2:1269005280834752542> <:blueheart:1252803082849488956>
